{"tid":2269984,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出爐艾美視帝Jeremy Strong關注香港：「他們很勇敢」","createTime":"2020-11-03T21:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T23:24:46.000Z","uid":310867,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0d76537dd41cb9fe6efd46ac26c8ec201cea9e","tid":2269984,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:03:22.000Z","msg":"剛於今年9月憑《傳媒家族繼承人》（Succession）獲得艾美獎視帝的Jeremy Strong，在當中飾演示威者領袖Jerry Rubin，現實中他同樣關心各地民主現況，在訪問中更提到香港：「這部電影的信息是歌頌和平示威，憑遊行去表達意見的分歧，也是去表達愛國的精神之一，去對抗壓制。我對所有示威者致敬，因為他們很勇敢，如果Jerry Rubin、Bobby Seale、Abbie Hoffman、Tom Hayden還在生的話，他們一定會到西雅圖、明尼阿波利斯、香港、白羅斯去示威。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201104/FLLJTWJBOFD4RIAC6TWTN237NI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201104%2FFLLJTWJBOFD4RIAC6TWTN237NI%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=8fc14bc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201104%2FFLLJTWJBOFD4RIAC6TWTN237NI%2F&h=d0f16ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201104/FLLJTWJBOFD4RIAC6TWTN237NI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnFhRWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnFhRWQ.png&h=b692cd53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqiWn3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqiWn3w.png&h=c4eab9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZuyqgS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZuyqgS.png&h=6a2a4a42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kqqgoy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kqqgoy.png&h=4724f9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQZZkQG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQZZkQG.png&h=055d3f66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CbE6Lhn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbE6Lhn.png&h=b517365d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2011年憑電影《社交網絡》（The Social Network）獲奧斯卡最佳編劇，其後轉型做導演，2017年憑首次自編自導的《莫莉遊戲》（Molly&rsquo;s Game）獲得奧斯卡最佳改編劇本提名，劇集代表作則有《白宮群英》（The West Wing）。"},{"pid":"96f0d9b69225b0fe3259a6173031e9b45abea60c","tid":2269984,"uid":310867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:05:51.000Z","msg":"套戲卡士仲有<br />\nMichael Keaton<br />\nEddie Redmayne<br />\nJoseph Gordon-Levitt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b17d6386f7e86ebc8cae25d228821ea9ebef106","tid":2269984,"uid":79117,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:06:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20feb33ac021dbbaed4d76b14200315ffbcf5e72","tid":2269984,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:08:22.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40342b9dce28bd1f17d0c243b50bbaef9c96211d","tid":2269984,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:12:46.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92cc9e398bf94c7c58fb697953c2a2476686121","tid":2269984,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T21:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb6b216df6105bcc8a97bdd